TY  - JOUR
TI  - Testing for Autocorrelation with Missing Observations
AU  - Savin, N. E.
AU  - White, Kenneth J.
AB  - [This paper considers procedures for testing for autocorrelation when there are missing observations on both the dependent and explanatory variables. These procedures include Durbin-Watson type tests given the vector of residuals, tests based on a set of uncorrelated residuals, and large sample likelihood ratio and Wald tests.]
