TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Bilinear Complementarity Problem and Competitive Equilibria of Piecewise Linear Economic Models
AU  - Wilson, Robert
AB  - [A parametric procedure for linear programming is shown to solve the bilinear complementarity problem, of which a special case is the problem of computing a competitive equilibrium of a piecewise linear economic model.]
