TY  - JOUR
TI  - Extermination of Self-Reproducible Natural Resources under Competitive Conditions
AU  - Hoel, Michael
AB  - [The present paper analyzes cropping of a self-reproducible natural resource under competitive conditions. Situations which may lead to extermination of the resource are described. In particular, it is shown that a production function with increasing returns to scale does not exclude the possibility of extermination, as suggested in [1].]
